    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that\u2019s been well-cared for. It runs like a dream and is ready for many more road trips! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and I\u2019m sure you will too. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
