    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road-wear consistent with careful use, while the interior remains smoke-free and crisp, featuring fully functional electronics and supple upholstery. Mechanically, it is in excellent shape; I have kept up with every scheduled service, including a recent oil change and a fresh set of premium tires. It shifts smoothly, brakes firmly, and offers a quiet, confident ride. This car has been garage-kept and loved, making it a turnkey option for a buyer who values both performance and peace of mind. Complete service records are available upon request.",
      "price": 36500.0,
