    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years\u2014perfect for anyone who wants a reliable, smooth-running car that still looks fantastic in the driveway. It\u2019s ready for a new home and many more adventures! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
