    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2008 Porsche Cayman S featuring the 3.4L M97 flat-six. This mid-engine platform delivers exceptional polar moment of inertia, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. Recent service includes a preventive water pump replacement and a full cooling system flush. The chassis retains its factory-tuned rigidity, equipped with PASM for variable damping. Braking is handled by four-piston monoblock calipers over vented rotors, showing minimal fade. While the exterior shows honest road use consistent with its enthusiast pedigree, the powertrain remains robust with linear torque and a healthy redline. A driver-spec example ready for the apex.",
